summary: An ordinance relating to the University of Washington Arboretum (Washington Park), authorizing an agreement with the Board of Regents of the University of Washington creating an "Arboretum Capital Improvement Trust Fund" as a depository for the proceeds of a condemnation award paid jointly to the University of Washington and the City of Seattle in King County Cause No. 597685 (Arboretum Interchange) pending use of such funds for arboretum capital improvement purposes.
